MMMMM----------------------JOHN ASH #JA9764---------------------------
    3/4 c  Sea salt
  2 1/2 qt Water
    1/3 c  Firmly packed brown sugar
      3 lg Garlic cloves, crushed
     12    Whole cloves
      1 ts Nutmeg, grated
  1 1/2 tb Crushed juniper berries
  3 1/2 lb Chicken
 
