           Degrees
    1/4 ts Dry yeast
      2 c  (about 9 ounces) unbleached,
           All-purpose flour or whole
           Wheat flour
           Sponge:
    3/4 c  Warm tap water, about 110
           Degrees
    1/2 ts Dry yeast
      1 c  Risen starter, above
