  1 3/4 lb Boned salmon fillet, with
           Skin, or steaks about
    3/4    Inch
           Thick
           Marinade:
      3 tb Soy sauce
      1 tb Sake, or dry sherry
      1 tb Mirin
      1 ts Fresh ginger juice
      3 tb Oil
      1 tb Mirin
      1 tb Sugar
           Sansho powder
